```

## Installation
#### Windows and linux
It is very easy to install melage on pc and laptop 
1. clone library

```sh
git clone [https://github.com/bahramjafrasteh/melage](https://github.com/bahramjafrasteh/melage) <br>
```
2. install requirements
```sh
pip install -r requirements.txt
```
3. run melage
```sh
python melage.py
```

